#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:276
msgid "Slope shading"
msgstr "Hyllerundertrykning"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:277
msgid ""
"The terrain can be shaded among slopes to indicate either wind direction, "
"sun position or a fixed shading from North-West."
msgstr ""
"Jorden kan undertrykkes mellem hyller til at indikere enten vindretning, "
"solposition eller et fast undertryk fra Vest-Nordvest."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:282
msgid "Terrain contrast"
msgstr "Hyllerskarpemal"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:283
msgid ""
"Defines the amount of Phong shading in the terrain rendering. Use large "
"values to emphasise terrain slope, smaller values if flying in steep "
"mountains."
msgstr ""
"Definerer mængden af Phong-undertryk i hyldesnittet. Brug store værdier for "
"at understrege hyldeslope, små værdier hvis man flyver i stive fjerner."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:289
msgid "Terrain brightness"
msgstr "Hyldelyst"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TerrainDisplayConfigPanel.cpp:290
msgid ""
"Defines the brightness (whiteness) of the terrain rendering. This controls "
"the average illumination of the terrain."
msgstr ""
"Definerer lysintensiteten (hvidhed) af hyldesnittet. Dette regulerer "
"gennemsnitligt lystråling på jorden."

