msgstr "[Full GPL License](xcsoar://dialog/credits)"

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:164
#, c-format
msgid ""
"# Getting Started\n"
"\n"
"To use XCSoar effectively, configure the following:\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Map and data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download maps, "
"waypoints, and airspace files for your region\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Set up your aircraft with "
"the correct polar curve\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Pilot info](xcsoar://config/logger) - Enter your name and weight\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Connect your flight instruments\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flights automatically to "
"WeGlide\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Show thermal "
"locations from thermalmap.info on the map\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Safety factors](xcsoar://config/safety) - Set arrival height, terrain "
"clearance and polar degradation\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Terrain display](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Choose terrain colors, "
"shading and contour lines\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(optional)* - Share your "
"position via SkyLines or LiveTrack24\n"
"\n"
"The easiest way to explore XCSoar is to [replay an existing IGC flight]"
"(xcsoar://dialog/replay)."
msgstr ""
"# Kom godt i gang\n"
"\n"
"For at bruge XCSoar effektivt skal du konfigurere følgende:\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Kort og data](xcsoar://config/site-files) - Download kort, waypoints "
"og luftrumsfiler for din region\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Aircraft polar](xcsoar://config/planes) - Indstil dit fly med den "
"korrekte polære kurve\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Pilotinfo](xcsoar://config/logger) - Indtast dit navn og vægt\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Devices](xcsoar://config/devices) - Tilslut dine flyinstrumenter\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide) - Upload flyafgange automatisk til "
"WeGlide\n"
"\n"
"- [%s] [Thermal Information Map](xcsoar://config/weather) - Vis termiske "
"steder fra thermalmap.info på kortet\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Sikkerhedsfaktorer](xcsoar://config/safety) - Indstil ankomsthøjde, "
"terrænfrihøjde og polar nedbrydning\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Terrænvisning](xcsoar://config/terrain) - Vælg terrænfarver, skygge "
"og konturlinjer\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] [Live tracking](xcsoar://config/tracking) *(valgfrit)* - Del din "
"position via SkyLines eller LiveTrack24\n"
"\n"
"Den nemmeste måde at udforske XCSoar på er at [afspille en eksisterende IGC-"
"flyvning](xcsoar://dialog/replay)."

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:202
msgid ""
"# Preflight Checks\n"
"\n"
"Before each flight, verify:\n"
"\n"
"1. **Plane & Polar** - Correct aircraft and polar selected. [Config > Plane]"
"(xcsoar://config/planes)\n"
"\n"
"2. **Flight parameters** - Wing loading, bugs, QNH, max temperature. [Info > "
"Flight](xcsoar://dialog/flight)\n"
"\n"
"3. **Wind** - Set wind manually or enable auto wind. [Info > Wind](xcsoar://"
"dialog/wind)\n"
"\n"
"4. **Task** - Create a task for navigation guidance. [Nav > Task Manager]"
"(xcsoar://dialog/task)"
msgstr ""
"# Preflight-tjek\n"
"\n"
"Før hver flyvning skal du kontrollere:\n"
"\n"
"1. **Plane & Polar** - Korrekt fly og polar valgt. [Config > Plane](xcsoar://"
"config/planes)\n"
"\n"
"2. **Flyveparametre** - Vingebelastning, fejl, QNH, max temperatur. [Info > "
"Flight](xcsoar://dialog/flight)\n"
"\n"
"3. **Vind** - Indstil vind manuelt eller aktiver automatisk vind. [Info > "
"Wind](xcsoar://dialog/wind)\n"
"\n"
"4. **Opgave** - Opret en opgave til navigationsvejledning. [Nav > Task "
"Manager](xcsoar://dialog/task)"

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:220
msgid ""
"# After Your Flight\n"
"\n"
"1. **Download logs** - Retrieve flight logs from your FLARM or logger "
"device. [Config > Devices](xcsoar://config/devices)\n"
"\n"
"2. **Analysis** - Review your flight statistics. [Info > Analysis](xcsoar://"
"dialog/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"3. **Status** - Check flight timing and statistics. [Info > Status](xcsoar://"
"dialog/status)\n"
"\n"
"4. **Upload** - Upload to WeGlide directly from XCSoar. Configure your "
"WeGlide User ID in [Config > System > WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide)"
msgstr ""
"# Efter din flyvning\n"
"\n"
"1. **Download logs** - Hent flylogs fra din FLARM eller logger enhed. "
"[Config > Devices](xcsoar://config/devices)\n"
"\n"
"2. **Analyse** - Gennemgå dine flystatistikker. [Info > Analysis](xcsoar://"
"dialog/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"3. **Status** - Tjek flyvetid og statistik. [Info > Status](xcsoar://dialog/"
"status)\n"
"\n"
"4. **Upload** - Upload til WeGlide direkte fra XCSoar. Konfigurer dit "
"WeGlide bruger-id i [Config > System > WeGlide](xcsoar://config/weglide)"

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:316
msgid ""
"![](resource:IDB_LOCATION_PIN)\n"
"\n"
"# Location Access\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar collects location data to enable flight navigation, thermal mapping, "
"and flight logging even when the app is closed or not in use.\n"
"\n"
"- **GPS Position** - Real-time navigation and glide computer\n"
"- **Background Location** - Continuous flight recording when the screen is "
"off or another app is in the foreground\n"
"- **Foreground Service** - Keeps GPS active during your flight\n"
"\n"
"Your location data is stored locally on your device. It is not shared unless "
"you explicitly enable tracking in [Config > Tracking](xcsoar://config/"
"tracking).\n"
"\n"
"[Privacy Policy](https://github.com/XCSoar/XCSoar/blob/master/PRIVACY.md)"
msgstr ""
"![](https://github.com/XCSoar/XCSoar/blob/master/PRIVACY.md)\n"
"\n"
"# Lokationsadgang\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar indsamler lokationsdata for at aktivere flynavigation, termisk "
"kortlægning og flylogning, selv når appen er lukket eller ikke er i brug.\n"
"\n"
"- **GPS-position** - Realtidsnavigation og glidecomputer\n"
"- **Baggrundsplacering** - Kontinuerlig flyoptagelse, når skærmen er "
"slukket, eller en anden app er i forgrunden\n"
"- **Forgrundsservice** - Holder GPS aktiv under din flyvning\n"
"\n"
"Dine placeringsdata gemmes lokalt på din enhed. Det deles ikke, medmindre du "
"udtrykkeligt aktiverer sporing i [Config > Tracking](xcsoar://config/"
"tracking).\n"
"\n"
"[Privacy Policy](resource:IDB_LOCATION_PIN)"

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:339
msgid ""
"![](resource:IDB_NOTIFICATION_BELL)\n"
"\n"
"# Notifications\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar needs notification permission to maintain a persistent notification "
"while recording your flight. This notification is required by Android for "
"background operation and provides a quick way to return to the app.\n"
"\n"
"Without this permission, Android may stop flight recording when the app is "
"in the background."
msgstr ""
"![](resource:IDB_NOTIFICATION_BELL)\n"
"\n"
"# Meddelelser\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar har brug for meddelelsestilladelse for at opretholde en vedvarende "
"meddelelse, mens du optager din flyvning. Denne meddelelse er påkrævet af "
"Android til baggrundsbetjening og giver en hurtig måde at vende tilbage til "
"appen.\n"
"\n"
"Uden denne tilladelse kan Android stoppe flyoptagelsen, når appen er i "
"baggrunden."

#: src/Dialogs/dlgQuickGuide.cpp:356
msgid ""
"# XCSoar Cloud\n"
"\n"
"The XCSoar project offers a service that allows sharing thermal and wave "
"locations with other pilots in real time.\n"
"\n"
"If you participate, your **position**, **thermal/wave locations** and other "
"weather data will be transmitted to the XCSoar Cloud server.\n"
"\n"
"You can change this at any time in [Config > Tracking](xcsoar://config/"
"tracking)."
msgstr ""
"# XCSoar Cloud\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar-projektet tilbyder en service, der gør det muligt at dele termiske og "
"bølgelokaliteter med andre piloter i realtid.\n"
"\n"
"Hvis du deltager, vil din **position**, **termiske/bølgeplaceringer** og "
"andre vejrdata blive transmitteret til XCSoar Cloud-serveren.\n"
"\n"
"Du kan til enhver tid ændre dette i [Config > Tracking](xcsoar://config/"
"tracking)."

