#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Gestiknavigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar understøtter berøringsbevægelser på kortet:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe op** (U): Zoom ind\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Stryg ned** (D): Zoom ud\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Stryg til højre** (R): Forrige "
"skærmtilstand\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Stryg til venstre** (L): Næste "
"skærmtilstand\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Op-Ned** (UD): Autozoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Ned-højre** (DR): Waypointdetaljer\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Ned-venstre** (DL): Alternativt\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Højre-ned** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Op-højre-ned** (URD): Analyse\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Venstre-Ned-Højre** (LDR): Tjekliste\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Op-højre-ned-venstre** (URDL): "
"Panoreringstilstand\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Venstre-Ned-Højre-Ned-Venstre** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Op-venstre-ned-højre** (ULDR): Hurtig "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Tryk længe på kortet for at gå ind i panoreringstilstand. Tryk på, mens du "
"er i panoreringstilstand for at se nærliggende waypoints."

