msgid ""
"MacCready speed-to-fly for optimal flight to the next waypoint. In cruise "
"flight mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for maintaining altitude. In "
"final glide mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for descent."
msgstr ""
"MacCready hastighed til flyve for optimalt flyve til næste vejpunkt. I "
"luftfartmodus beregnes denne flyvehastighed for at holde på højden. I "
"slutglid modus beregnes denne flyvehastighed for at desender."

