"with estimated arrival time greater than AAT time plus 5 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Udenfor skuespil og kan snibe nu med estimerede ankomsttid, hvis den er mere "
"end 5 minutter over AAT-tiden."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thermal average over all"
msgstr "Gennemsnitlig termik"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "T Avg"
msgstr "T Gnsn"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:625
#, no-c-format
